          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A Mac app built with Mac Catalyst that uses the Mac user interface idiom displays a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiswitch"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " as a checkbox when the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiswitch/3621874-preferredstyle"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " value is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiswitchstyle/uiswitchstyleautomatic"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (the default value) or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiswitchstyle/uiswitchstylecheckbox"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If your app doesnâ€™t use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiuserinterfaceidiom/uiuserinterfaceidiommac"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " idiom, the switch appears as a slider switch. To learn more, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/mac_catalyst/choosing_a_user_interface_idiom_for_your_mac_app"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "level": 3,
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Add Text to the Checkbox",
          "anchor": "3682458"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To display text alongside the checkbox, set the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiswitch/3621876-title"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "codeListing",
          "code": [
            "let showFavoritesAtTop = UISwitch()",
            "showFavoritesAtTop.title = \"Always show favorite recipes at the top\""
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "3682456",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        },
